Gonzalo Higuain opened the scoring for Napoli in the 15th minute at the Volkswagen Arena . 
  Marek Hamsik doubled the visitors lead in the 23rd minute . 
  Nicklas Bendtner pulled a goal back for Wolfsburg in the 80th minute . 
  Manolo Gabbiadini made it 4-0 after coming on as a second-half substitute . 
  Rafa Benitez's side are in the semi-finals of the Europa League . 
 